hopobject.body: I'm interested in professional nursing and medical consultants ltd Savor a plain jane Margherita (dubbed âThe Queen,â $10). Free of blingy toppings, this naked pie is forced to prove its mettle, and does so with ease. The crisp, yet chewy crust and creamy, house-made mozzarella have perfect consistency from edge to center. Spicy sopressata ($16) adds a porky jumble of thick, meaty coins to the party and finishes with a restrained drizzle of local honey that tempers the heat while adding an alluring twist. A novel Brussels sprout option ($14) pairs with egg and truffle oil to make a seriously decadent vegetarian pie.
